twitch_info.title: I Wanna Potato 2.5: Whispers of the Needle Gods - Part 1
twitch_info.description: Great game, and finally great progress! Been a blast and joy to play, outside of occasional terrible segments or overwhelming difficulty spikes. Would recommend, but only to Post K3 players or equivalent experience.
